08/01/2008
BUCHAREST, Romania -- NATO Secretary-General Jaap de Hoop Scheffer will visit Bucharest on Friday (January 11th) to check on Romania's preparations for hosting the Alliance's April summit, local media reported on Monday.
This will be de Hoop Scheffer's second visit, as part of summit preparations.
The first occurred in October.
(Gandul - 08/01/08;
Rompres, Mediafax - 07/01/08)
